Compilation:
Build the skeleton code and run it.
cd A0
premake4 gmake
make
./A0

Manual:
Features added include
1) Blue and Green color sliders
2) Rotation slider
3) '+' and '-' keys scale the size of the triangle up and down respectively, each keypress changing scale by 0.1
4) 'R' key resets triangle
 
Inlcluded math.h for the value of pi to set rotational limit.
